snippet.title: Gas Guzzlers Extreme - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Gas Guzzlers Extreme on Steam: 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/243800/

Gas Guzzlers Extreme on Xbox: 
https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/gas-guzzlers-extreme/brqh5gkv7912

Gas Guzzlers Extreme is a fast, furious, armed-to-the-teeth, trigger-happy shooter, shifted into top gear! Take a white knuckle ride in this crazily addictive combat racing game. 

Looking for more information on Gas Guzzlers Extreme? Check out the following channels:
